description:
After winning her first match she fell to the veteran
Jester; however, the Deceptacon is strong and learns
fast. With two matches under her belt, she is looking
for another win and to move up in the rankings.
The Grappler showed serious skills against the
Scorpion, but it is hard to gauge her true ability
since the Scorpion holds the record for losing at US.
Add to that the Grappler's other win against Kat, and
we still do not have a standard to judge the Grappler
by. The one thing I do know with certainty is that the
Grappler has a mad strap on technique, and really
knows
how to dish out a rd4 fucking.
title: The Deceptacon (1-1) The Grappler (2-2)
